MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: apps/client/src/cartridges/.+\.tsx?$
MATCH_CONTENT: (className[^"'`]*["'][^"'`]*(skin-[a-z]|bg-glass|text-glow)|var\(--(pulse|vivid)-)
ADVISORY: |
  Cartridge files must stay shell-agnostic. Banned tokens: `skin-*`, `bg-glass`,
  `text-glow`, `var(--pulse-*)`, `var(--vivid-*)`. Use the `--po-*` contract
  instead — see `apps/client/src/shells/pulse/pulse-theme.css` for the keys.
  If you need a tone that isn't mapped, extend `--po-*` in ALL shell theme files
  (classic, vivid, pulse). Never inline a shell-specific token in a cartridge.
